    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0152回】　合気道の鍛錬目標</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0101-0200/t-0152-aiki-true-goal/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
